                                                                                              PE-15           WATER DAMAGE PROTECTION
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              PE-15[01]             the system is protected from damage resulng from water leakage by providing
                                                                                                                                    master shutoﬀ or isolaon valves;

                                                                                                              PE-15[02]             the master shutoﬀ or isolaon valves are accessible;

                                                                                                              PE-15[03]             the master shutoﬀ or isolaon valves are working properly;

                                                                                                              PE-15[04]             the master shutoﬀ or isolaon valves are known to key personnel.

